videos.headline: Florida State goes out in front on Terry's 43-yard TD
videos.description: Alex Hornibrook hits Tamorrion Terry on the slant, and Terry runs 43 yards for the Seminoles' touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Florida State goes out in front on Terry's 43-yard TD) 2019/09/28

videos.headline: Hornibrook goes deep to Wilson for Florida State's TD
videos.description: Alex Hornibrook throws the deep ball to Ontaria Wilson for the 40-yard Seminoles' touchdown.

videos.headline: Terry hauls in his 2nd TD for FSU
videos.description: Tamorrion Terry grabs the nine-yard touchdown pass from Alex Hornibrook to increase Florida State's lead to 24-6 vs. NC State.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Terry hauls in his 2nd TD for FSU) 2019/09/28
